{"tid":1389762,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生查詢及申請做陪審員","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:57:35.000Z","uid":268061,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3508ad447dae2e0ce2ab52aeaf6851abbc96af07","tid":1389762,"uid":268061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"大學生申請做陪審員<br />\n1/ 首先要打電話去 陪審員查詢熱線: 2825 4668, CHECK自己係唔係陪審員名單<br />\n2/ 如果唔係, 可以打去入境處 陪審團登記小組: 2829 3356<br />\n<br />\n登記程序如下, 需要3樣文件, 如下:  ( 即A+B+C )<br />\nA) 寫一封信, 內容話想登記成為陪審員, 包括要有:<br />\n- 中文 和 英文全名 (跟香港身份證一樣)<br />\n- 香港身份證號碼<br />\n- 記得要簽名<br />\n----------------------範本如下:-------------------------<br />\n致: 陪審團登記小組<br />\n<br />\n本人 陳大文 (CHAN TAI MAN), HKID: A123456(7) 現想申請成為陪審員, 現附上表格ROP18 和 最高學歷文件副本, 如有問題, 請致電 9123 9123與本人聯絡.<br />\n           <br />\n<ins>(你個簽名)            </ins><br />\n陳大文<br />\n2019-07-31<br />\n ---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nB) 到入境處網站下載表格 (ROP18) 並填寫<br />\n- <a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fforms%2Fforms%2Frop18.html&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047IjxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=7fc07d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html</a><br />\n<br />\nC) 最高學歷文件副本<br />\n<br />\n請預備好 A)信, B) 表格ROP18 &amp; C) 最高學歷文件副本, 一併寄回到以下地址:<br />\n<br />\n香 港 灣 仔 告 士 打 道 七 號<br />\n入 境 事 務 大 樓 1 2 0 1 室<br />\n陪 審 團 登 記 小 組 收<br />\n<br />\n結果將會在大概一個月內以信面通知回覆"},{"pid":"16c02d764821c78ad474be47f6724039123adc24","tid":1389762,"uid":104165,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"陪審員唔係自動入pool架咩?<br />\n如果而家大量人寫信去想做陪審, 係人都知你咩底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c76a25fe1535fad3958dcffacab40fae6f54f2","tid":1389762,"uid":268061,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"16c02d764821c78ad474be47f6724039123adc24","tid":1389762,"uid":104165,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"陪審員唔係自動入pool架咩?<br />\n如果而家大量人寫信去想做陪審, 係人都知你咩底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"GRAD左成5年, 岩岩打左去問, 先知自己唔係個POOL入面,  你想點做, 你自己去考慮, 我做法係, 入紙仲有一絲希望, 唔入既, 就一定冇機會."},{"pid":"1d194895d34ffdcd107f3bbb45101aaa66a37794","tid":1389762,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"重要，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23bdf82bde87233774d6c9ac458840f64e69abe","tid":1389762,"uid":51747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"一直以為自動，好似一畢業就收到信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1408125553b3d3c2386812be2ceab1bebc0d2d2f","tid":1389762,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"grad左廿年<br />\n<br />\n先抽中一次<br />\n仲要嗰日無案報到都唔駛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁易抽中"},{"pid":"5add6493f79014f966e9365027d05b39d56a33fb","tid":1389762,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"岩岩check左自己係個list內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6eb8f59ba82ee7d8d6a0f4e4090d37274ded89","tid":1389762,"uid":259419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4ee58a3bfc0143240a8913517906aaa273b24848","tid":1389762,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人 check 下自己入唔入list"},{"pid":"83b4777e38f317f15c1cb4017df7d6a51d52dd5d","tid":1389762,"uid":272518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"大學畢業 但 唔係list到...<br />\n打左去問, 又叫我打去入境處<br />\n樓主張form 好似係更改資料form, 唔係登記 form"},{"pid":"50fd85b87af5018690f8afb42f7be54e99